- if @person.trusteenumber == "Three" && @person.co2_3 == "Yes"
  <married>I name #{@person.name} as my personal representative. If #{@person.name} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my successor personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethesecond} and #{@person.trusteethethird} as my successor co-personal representatives. If either #{@person.trusteethesecond} or #{@person.trusteethethird} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name the other as my sole successor personal representative. If neither #{@person.trusteethesecond} nor #{@person.trusteethethird} is able or willing to serve, then I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative.

- elsif @person.trusteenumber == "Three"
  If neither of us can serve as trustee because of resignation, incapacity, or death, I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethesecond} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethesecond} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethethird} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethethird} is unable or unwilling to serve, then I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative.
- elsif @person.trustee.number == "four"
